{"tid":2164973,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"肥媽老公有肺炎，大家有咩說話安慰下佢？","createTime":"2020-08-19T13:36:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-20T05:01:59.000Z","uid":97435,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"307d42c934aa709e0d3e82ee6ea433a8936ce436","tid":2164973,"uid":97435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T13:36:27.000Z","msg":"過去肥媽不時拍片和大家分享煮食心得，惟近日肥媽昨日在網上分享片段表示自己身在醫院，原來老公因為<strong><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">肺炎和血管閉塞</span></span></strong>入院。<br />\n<br />\n身在病房的肥媽表示過去收到不少朋友關心她老公的情況，於是拍片和大家報平安。她在片中介紹病房環境，表示自己把房間分成有工作間、廚房、士多房。<br />\n<br />\n她表示每7日做一次病毒測試，就連房門也不能踏出，因為擔心房外多細菌。她說︰「我入嚟之前要撩鼻（鼻液測試）&hellip;&hellip;上個禮拜我真係癲，睇到老公辛苦，我都頭痛，今朝醫生話佢樣樣都好，佢好有胃口，睇佢瞓到好似BB咁，我就舒服，所以人要活在當下。」她透露老公將於<span class=\"large\">下星期出院</span>，屆時他會<span class=\"large\"><span class=\"red\">親自和大家道謝</span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n蔬ce:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.am730.com.hk/news/share/231484\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.am730.com.hk%2Fnews%2Fshare%2F231484&d=MYvC0VRZm9a3oqKPvUvInGLZ6li1RkmcNQmTobTGNbY%3D&h=6c0f1471\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.am730.com.hk/news/share/231484</a>"},{"pid":"47e4ba726e7eb2b0a72bbebd8c68cb7826847c74","tid":2164973,"uid":325011,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T13:42:24.000Z","msg":"返大灣區醫喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd3098720f43c5eee774589ddf3a38ad2b11317e","tid":2164973,"uid":295650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"307d42c934aa709e0d3e82ee6ea433a8936ce436","tid":2164973,"uid":97435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T13:36:27.0